SUMMARY:Sonomacana at Rio Nido Roadhouse
DESCRIPTION:Beginning as a hastag and a dream\, Kyle Martin started using the moniker “Sonomacana” to represent the way music sounds in Sonoma County while he blogged and hosted his radio show “Kyle’s Calendar.” Over the years\, he began to embrace the genre of Sonomacana as his own\, and decided to form a group dedicated to the cause of spreading the good sounds of Sonoma County. \nWhile Sonomacana has taken many forms as has worked with many artists\, the core of the group consists of Lara Brown on vocals\, flute\, ukulele\, and percussion; Kyle Martin on vocals\, guitar/bass\, melodica and percussion; and Dave McLean\, lead guitarist extraordinaire. \nSonomacana explores the sounds of rock\, ska\, and reggae with a Sonoma County twist! Specializing in good vibes and immaculate taste\, their blend of originals and covers ensures you’ll leave your worries at the door and move to the beat of our loving ambition. \nJoin Sonomacana for a show\, and you’ll hear songs that are over 100 years old and songs playing on the radio.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/sonomacana-at-rio-nido-roadhouse/
LOCATION:Rio Nido Roadhouse\, 14540 Canyon 2 Road\, Rio Nido\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
GEO:38.5205;-122.979
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Rio Nido Roadhouse 14540 Canyon 2 Road Rio Nido CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=14540 Canyon 2 Road:geo:-122.979,38.5205
END:VEVENT
