SUMMARY:Peter Filice at Adobe Road Winery
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a special Saturday acoustic live music set at Adobe Road Winery in downtown Petaluma. Sip on award-winning wines while enjoying talented local musicians in a warm and inviting atmosphere. Choose from wines by the glass or bottle to discover new favorites. Reserve your spot on Tock and make it a memorable night of great music\, fine wine\, and good company! \nAbout Peter Filice\nA lifelong vocalist and guitar player\, Peter has been in the Bay Area music scene since the 1990’s. He was vocalist and guitarist for the South Bay band OTR\, winners of the KFOX Last Band Standing competition in 2010\, and subsequently\, in 2015\, started a very successful acoustic act\, P.S. Acoustic Music\, performing in solo\, duo\, and trio formats at numerous South Bay venues. He also has performed in tribute shows to Creedence Clearwater Revival\, Three Dog Night\, Linda Ronstadt\, and his own Simon and Garfunkel tribute. Having recently relocated to Petaluma\, Peter is now performing at many North Bay venues as well as maintaining shows in the South Bay.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/peter-filice-at-adobe-road-winery/
LOCATION:Adobe Road Winery\, 6 Petaluma Blvd N\, Petaluma\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
GEO:38.234020;-122.639530
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Adobe Road Winery 6 Petaluma Blvd N Petaluma CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=6 Petaluma Blvd N:geo:-122.639530,38.234020
END:VEVENT
