SUMMARY:The Joni Mitchell Situation
DESCRIPTION:Come in from the rainy cold and be dazzled by the energy and emotion of Joni Mitchell’s songwriting brilliance! From the raw simplicity of her tunes from “Blue” to the social/ecological musical honesty of “Shine;” from the the playful jazz-inspired longing of “Court and Spark” to the genre-bending soulful journey of “Hejira;” we bring you this luscious music live! \nSaturday\, February 28\, 5:30-8:30. Kate Foley-Beining on vocals\, piano\, dulcimer\, and guitar with Sonoma County jazz greats: Tom Shader\, bass; Kevin Dillon\, drums; Christian Foley-Beining\, guitar. \nFurthermore Wine and Music Lounge\, 328 Healdsburg Ave. Healdsburg\, CA.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/the-joni-mitchell-situation-3/
LOCATION:Furthermore Wines – Healdsburg\, 328 Healdsburg Ave\, Healdsburg\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
