SUMMARY:Smoke & Mirrors at Coyote Sonoma
DESCRIPTION:Smoke & Mirrors are a 5 piece Electrica\, Acoustic & Percussion band with a deep bench of musicians to fit the wide range of genres they cover\, accenting harmonies. Covering Doo-wop\, R&B\, Rock\, Country\, and Folk all with a little twist – featuring music from artists such as the Isly Bros\, The Belmonts\, Beatles\, Eagles\, Del Shannon\, Stones\, CSNY\, CCR\, Ricky Nelson\, Romantics\, Marshal Tucker\, Lynyrd Skynyrd\, Doobie Bros\,\, Otis Redding\, Kenny Chesney\, Paul Simon\, The Beegees\, and many more!
