SUMMARY:The Cherry Pickers- Reunion Show at Elephant in the Room
DESCRIPTION:The Cherry Pickers’ are a contemporary bluegrass band playing your favourite tunes from today and back in the day. Always on the search to “uncover” some hidden bluegrass in any song\, their tasty arrangements are reverent to Bluegrass tradition. Coupled with their love of traditional tunes and their original songs\, the Cherry Pickers make for an exciting and refreshing bluegrass experience. The Cherry Pickers appear regularly around Adelaide and have played at many festivals around the country including the National Bluegrass Festival\, Mountain Grass\, the Kelly Country Pick\, JamGrass \, the Fleurieu Folk Festival\, Healesville Festival\, Cullulleraine\, Groundwater\, Dorrigo Folk Festival and the Wirinna Bluegrass Festival. In 2016\, the Cherry Pickers toured the US including playing at AmericaFest in Nashville Tennessee. \nThe Cherry Pickers are: \nMark Bandick – Guitar\, vocals\nPaul Cooper – Banjo\, vocals\nRob Cooper – Dobro\, vocals\nLou Evangelistis – Mandolin\, vocals\nMae Napier-Traeger – Fiddle\, vocals\nGage Stead – Bass\, vocals
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/the-cherry-pickers-reunion-show-at-elephant-in-the-room/
LOCATION:Elephant in the Room\, 177A Healdsburg Avenue\, Healdsburg\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
