SUMMARY:Electric Funeral- Tattoos & Blues - Day Two
DESCRIPTION:Electric Funeral brings the heavy Ozzy era Black Sabbath experience to Tattoos & Blues on Feb 28 at Vintage Space. Heavy riffs all night.\nTattoos & Blues rolls into Saturday with Electric Funeral\, the Classic Black Sabbath Experience that channels the raw power of the Ozzy years. This is the sound that reshaped heavy music. Thunderous riffs\, ominous grooves\, soaring vocals and that unmistakable Sabbath weight delivered with accuracy\, attitude and plenty of volume. \nElectric Funeral leans into the early catalog that defined the genre. War Pigs\, Iron Man\, Paranoid\, N.I.B.\, Fairies Wear Boots and the deep cuts that true fans love. The band captures the spirit of the original era with thick guitars\, a heavy rhythm section and vocals that cut straight through the room. \nIf you grew up on the dark\, hypnotic pulse of Black Sabbath or you’ve only heard the legends\, this show brings the experience to life inside the intimate glow of Vintage Space. It’s the perfect pairing for a night
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/electric-funeral-tattoos-blues-day-two/
LOCATION:Vintage Space at The Flamingo Resort\, 2777 Fourth St.\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
GEO:38.45182;-122.68916
