SUMMARY:Coffey Park - Classic Rock - Downtown Santa Rosa
DESCRIPTION:Classic rock fans\, this one’s for you. Coffey Park brings the greatest hits of the 60s\, 70s\, and 80s to the stage at Barrel Proof Lounge in Downtown Santa Rosa.\nKnown as Sonoma County’s favorite cover band\, Coffey Park delivers crowd-pleasing rock classics with tight musicianship and high-energy performances. The band features PJ Malone (vocals/percussion)\, Michael Grieco (guitars)\, Walter Edwards (guitars/vocals)\, Michael Lunt (bass/vocals)\, and Brad Hoffman (drums/vocals).\nSaturday\, February 28\n8pm\nNo cover\n501 Mendocino Ave\, Downtown Santa Rosa\n21+\nGrab a drink\, bring some friends\, and enjoy a night of timeless rock hits in the heart of Downtown Santa Rosa.\nCheck out www.BarrelProofLounge.com for all sorts of good times ahead!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/coffey-park-classic-rock-downtown-santa-rosa/
LOCATION:Barrel Proof Lounge\, 501 Mendocino Avenue\, Santa Rosa\, CA
